<p>Our aim and vision</p>

<p>“Every deserving student will get education, We dont care how long it will take or how much energy it will take, but we can promise  one thing that together one day we can put a positive impact towards the society” – Mayush Ayush [Owner &amp; Founder]</p>

<p> </p>

<p>Knowledge is the most powerful weapon that one can have. So, we aim to make India more powerful by sharing the gift of knowledge from those who supply it to those who need it. Knowledge is not something to hide its a blessing to share</p>

<p>                  Our aim is to  provide the users the best and easy to access free platform that will bind them with Booksbear forever. We want to be their first choice for donating,renting &amp; buying books</p>

<p>                  Proudly we are indias first platform to having all these feature at a same place and the most convenient and easy to use and easily accessable platform, we are not here to maximising the profit , we are here to put  a positive impact in the society.</p>";